docs {
  ## Omedia.city API
  
  Bruno collection for querying Predecesspr player statistics using the Omeda.city API; alternatively see communit Postman collection: <https://www.postman.com/dewaldels/public/request/jq6ee5j/players-player-id>
  
  Public API mirror: <https://pred.saibotu.de/api/public/get-matches-since/0/>
}
